---
// FeaturesSection — bento grid of feature cards
---

<section class="features">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-label reveal">Core Strengths</p>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal">The contract layer between intent,<br/>code, and delivery.</h2>

    <div class="bento">
      <div class="bento-card bento-graph reveal" style="--reveal-delay: 0s">
        <div class="bento-label">Verifiable Graph</div>
        <h3>One graph for requirements, designs, tasks, and evidence.</h3>
        <p>Every document becomes a typed node with computed reverse links. Evidence flows in through native Rust and Vitest support, tags, or file globs. Query any slice with the CLI or <a href="/explore/" style="color: var(--gold); text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 2px;">explore the graph interactively</a> in your browser.</p>
        <div class="bento-visual graph-mini" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 240 120">
            <g class="graph-edges" stroke-width="1">
              <line x1="120" y1="30" x2="60" y2="60"/>
              <line x1="120" y1="30" x2="180" y2="60"/>
              <line x1="60" y1="60" x2="40" y2="95"/>
              <line x1="60" y1="60" x2="90" y2="95"/>
              <line x1="180" y1="60" x2="160" y2="95"/>
              <line x1="180" y1="60" x2="210" y2="95"/>
            </g>
            <circle class="graph-root" cx="120" cy="30" r="4.5"/>
            <circle class="graph-mid" cx="60" cy="60" r="3.5"/>
            <circle class="graph-mid" cx="180" cy="60" r="3.5"/>
            <circle class="graph-leaf" cx="40" cy="95" r="3"/>
            <circle class="graph-leaf" cx="90" cy="95" r="3"/>
            <circle class="graph-leaf" cx="160" cy="95" r="3"/>
            <circle class="graph-leaf" cx="210" cy="95" r="3"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bento-card bento-ai reveal" style="--reveal-delay: 0.08s">
        <div class="bento-label">Agent Contract & CI Guardrails</div>
        <h3>Structured scope for coding agents. Verified in CI.</h3>
        <p>Six agent skills ship with Supersigil, teaching agents the full spec-driven workflow: specification, implementation, refactoring, retroactive documentation, CI review, and end-to-end development. Agents load context, plan against criteria, and re-verify through the same CLI. <code>supersigil verify</code> checks the graph in CI, while tracked files flag specs that need review after code changes.</p>
        <div class="bento-snippet" aria-hidden="true">
          <code><span class="c-muted">$</span> supersigil context auth/req --format json</code>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bento-card bento-editor reveal" style="--reveal-delay: 0.16s">
        <div class="bento-label">Editor Integration</div>
        <h3>Specs rendered with live verification status.</h3>
        <p><a href="/guides/editor-setup/" style="color: var(--gold); text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 2px;">VS Code and IntelliJ extensions</a> render Markdown previews with verification badges, expandable evidence with test links, and navigation to related documents. Plus diagnostics, autocomplete, hover docs, and go-to-definition through the LSP server.</p>
        <div class="bento-visual" aria-hidden="true">
          <img src="/images/spec-rendering.webp" alt="Editor preview with verification badges and evidence details" style="width: 100%; border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid var(--border);"/>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .features {
    padding: 8rem 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .bento {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    grid-template-rows: auto auto;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    grid-template-areas:
      "graph  ai"
      "editor editor";
  }
  .bento-graph    { grid-area: graph; }
  .bento-ai       { grid-area: ai; }
  .bento-editor   { grid-area: editor; }

  .bento-card {
    padding: 2rem;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    transition: border-color 0.3s, background 0.3s;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .bento-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--border-hover);
    background: var(--bg-card-hover);
  }
  .bento-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .bento-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.35;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }
  .bento-card p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .bento-snippet {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    padding: 0.6rem 0.8rem;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.76rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    overflow: hidden;
    word-break: break-word;
  }
  .bento-snippet .c-muted { color: var(--text-dim); }
  .bento-snippet .c-gold { color: var(--gold); }
  .bento-snippet .c-teal { color: #5a8f9f; }
  .bento-snippet .c-str { color: #a8c97a; }
  .bento-snippet .c-red { color: #d45b5b; }
  :global([data-theme='light']) .bento-snippet {
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
  }
  .bento-visual {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }
  .graph-mini svg {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 240px;
  }
  .graph-edges { stroke: var(--gold); opacity: 0.45; }
  .graph-root  { fill: var(--gold); }
  .graph-mid   { fill: var(--teal); }
  .graph-leaf  { fill: var(--text-muted); }
</style>
